com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang

Interface TensorList

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GpuTensorList, TensorArray

    public interface TensorList
    This abstract data container is used to pass data between NNLayer components. It potentially represents data stored off-heap, such as on a particular GPU. Use of this abstract class allows optimizations where adjacent GPU components can operate with minimal CPU-GPU data transfer.
